  "body": "Hi all,\r\n\r\nCurrently our beacon state is a wrapper around an old beacon state protobuf object as we did not want to break backwards compatibility and old chain DB's. In preparation for a network restart, we should deprecate our old beacon state protobuf completely and just use the new state for everything in the beacon chain.",
