    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This might complicate database storage as all of our database objects are protobuf messages. One requirement is that ssz.Encode is significantly faster than proto.Marshal.\r\n\r\nAt the moment, with a generic ssz.Marshal, we could not move forward on this.\r\n\r\n```\r\nBenchmarkSszEncoding-8                       424           2569792 ns/op\r\nBenchmarkProtoEncoding-8                   29558             43455 ns/op\r\n```\r\n\r\nMarking this as blocked until we have a custom SSZ #4738 and we have updated benchmarks to compare. ",
